      • prepareDownloadUrl

        URL prepareDownloadUrl(@Nonnull
                     Identifier identifier,
                     @Nullable
                     String type,
                     @Nullable
                     Map<String,Object> parameters,
                     @Nullable
                     Locale locale)
        Returns the full URL to download requested resource content.
        Parameters:
        identifier - the unique (root) identifier of the resource
        type - the requested content type to be downloaded (already part of the request header) or null to expect default
        parameters - the optional resource parameters
        locale - the optional language the client has configured to prefer in results if applicable (already part of the request header if any)
        Returns:
        the full download path
